Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 11:17:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ARM/ARM64: defconfig: enable DRM_PANEL_TDO_DSI_V1

Share panel drivers to bcmxxx_defconfig as module to use in all.

Signed-off-by: kun_liu <kun_liu@shtdo.com>
